des:
Rock paper scissors is a hand game usually played between two people, in which each player forms one of three shapes with an outstretched hand. 
These shapes are rock, paper, and scissors. 
In this you challenge alexa in fun game and improve your ranking. 
to start game just say Alexa ,"open rock paper scissors"
